  "text": "At one time space in what is your past. There was a population of third density beings upon a planet which dwelt within your solar system. There are various names by which this planet has been named the vibratory sound complex, most usually used by your peoples is more deck. These entities destroying their planetary sphere, thus were forced to find room for themselves upon this third intensity, which is the only one in your solar system at their time space present, which was hospitable and capable of offering the lessons necessary to decrease their mind, body, spirit, and distortions with respect to the law of one.",
